data.text:
Dorothy Granger (November 21, 1911 - January 4, 1995) (age 83) was an actress who appeared in only 2 Three Stooges episodes in 1934 and 1938. Before she appeared with the Three Stooges in only those episodes, she appeared in a Curly Howard Solo in 1934. After she appeared with the Three Stooges in only those 2 episodes with them, she appeared in 3 Joe DeRita Solos of 1 in 1946 and 2 in 1947. She died from cancer.

Appearances with the Three Stooges:[]

Punch Drunks (1934), and Termites of 1938 (1938).

[]
